olutions-airtag-8bitdo-deal-sale" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/1/2/24022374/apple-watch-se-smartwatch-newyears-resolutions-airtag-8bitdo-deal-sale</id><author><name>安东尼奥·G·迪·贝内代托</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-01-02T11:44:11-05:00</published><updated> 2024-01-02T11:44:11-05:00</updated><title> Dish Network 重新加入 EchoStar，试图参与 5G 竞争</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;白色和红色背景的 Dish 徽标插图。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/Aa0syCUlLPm8IZaVndlgurjlZxw=/0x0:3000x2000/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73016476/acastro_STK052_01.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;插图由 Alex Castro / The Verge 绘制&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;ti7DCU&quot;>;EchoStar Corporation &lt;a href=&quot;https://go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp ;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hughes.com%2Fresources%2Fpress-releases%2Fechostar-corporation-completes-merger-dish-network-corporation&amp;amp;referrer=theverge.com&amp;amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww .theverge.com%2F2024%2F1%2F2%2F24022413%2Fdish-network-echostar-acquisition-5g-boost-mobile-wireless&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;今天宣布&lt;/a>; 12 月的最后一天完成了对 Dish Network 的收购。 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/8/8/23824206/dish-network-5g-satellite-merger&quot;>;两家公司于 8 月宣布合并&lt;/a>;后，Dish现在是“EchoStar 的全资子公司”，为什么？ 5G，亲爱的读者。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;rMVEfT&quot;>;Dish Network 一直被称为 EchoStar，直到 2008 年才更名为 Dish，并以 EchoStar 的名义剥离其卫星互联网业务。近年来，Dish 已&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/6/15/23762646/dish-network-june-2023-boost-fcc-p​​opulation-coverage-5g-genesis&quot; >;购买后转向 5G&lt;/a>; Boost Mobile&lt;/a>; 并启动 Project Genesis，从概念上讲，该项目将提供第四个大型网络，在美国与 AT&amp;T、Verizon 和 T-Mobile 竞争。截至 2022 年末，当我们最后一次对其进行测试时，它 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2022/11/24/23445995/dish-5g-network-genesis-las-vegas-Trial&quot; >;还不太令人印象深刻&lt;/a>;。&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-le